{"tid":2327630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【正視聽！！！】全港7624名武肺患者, 15至39歲 有2672位, 當中有1024為輸入個案","createTime":"2020-12-16T07:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T08:08:05.000Z","uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73b23cfd9b04ff7a26f9398b00069b59cb29ad24","tid":2327630,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"立會秘書處研究 15至39歲確診最多 佔35%<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2325757\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2325757</a><br />\n<br />\n見到呢個PO<br />\n年齡層完全亂鳩咁比較 <br />\n之𤔀download左政府數據做分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Flocal_situation_covid19_tc.pdf&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=d6c019f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n基於12月15日數據<br />\n全港7624名武肺患者<br />\n&lt;=14歲有418位, 當中有138位為輸入個案    (年齡層 = 14-0 = 14)<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">15-39歲有2672位, 當中有1024位為輸入個案  <ins>(年齡層 = 39-15 = 24)</ins></span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">40-59歲有2486位, 當中有409位為輸入個案<ins>(年齡層 = 59-40 = 19)</ins></span></strong></span> <br />\n60-79歲有1754位, 當中有141位為輸入個案 (年齡層 = 59-40 = 19)<br />\n&gt;=80歲有294位, 當中有7位為輸入個案<br />\n<br />\n另外基於平齡層做左個公平少少既分析<br />\n&lt;=19歲有748位, 當中有331位為輸入個案 (年齡層 = 19-0 = 19)<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">20-39歲有2324位, 當中有831位為輸入個案</span></strong></span> (年齡層 = 39-20=19)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">20-39歲確診根本少過40-59歲，輸入個案仲要佔撚左勁撚多，因為留學生</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YpavVYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpavVYH.jpg&h=53f49c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個分析極度BIAS<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立法會秘書處你做秘書做乜鳩野數據分析呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6615393f23574b6970856c4a5300e64f4de444f7","tid":2327630,"uid":196222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"計本地個案<br />\n20 至 39 係少過 60至79<br />\n而40 至 59係最多"},{"pid":"7a21d6c81aecfb8be9768cc129a7c84cbd97c9bb","tid":2327630,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gri4X1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gri4X1.png&h=5c3efe2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"613b74a98598900dd635a2e482ffdd0a304575e2","tid":2327630,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nA35XD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nA35XD.png&h=66475ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來衛生處都有資料<br />\n但垃圾會秘書處唔拎黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7a21d6c81aecfb8be9768cc129a7c84cbd97c9bb","tid":2327630,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gri4X1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gri4X1.png&h=5c3efe2d&s={SIZE}\" />"}}